     Start coding your AI agent
     ##agent.py creat with the ollama 
     from strands import Agent 
     from strands.models.ollama import OllamaModel   #conncet to the ollama 
     #By default it runs Amazon bedrock in the Background.(Amazon bedrock it the service form aws which gen ai can created and in  background work with LLM's)
     ollamaModel_model=OllamaModel(
     host="http://localhost:11434", #ollama server address 
     model_id="llama3.2:1b"            #Specify which model to use 
)
agent = Agent(model=ollamaModel_model)
 #create an instance of Agent 


 Run it with:  
  python agent.py                        
Your AI agent environment is ready!


2: install ollama for run LLM's locally. 
